headline: WK Kellogg confirms employee data breach tied to Cleo file-transfer flaw
summary: The Michigan-based breakfast cereal company confirmed it used Cleo as a vendor for human resources data.

headline: Texas announces probe into WK Kellogg’s ‘healthy’ claims
summary: According to the Attorney General’s office, several WK Kellogg cereals “are filled with petroleum-based artificial food colourings”.
